title: Cascading parameter values not displayed properly in HTML viewer
description: Cascading parameter values are not being displayed correctly in the HTML viewer.
OB: When selecting the first parameter value, the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group should be displayed. However, it is not currently displayed.
EB: The cascading parameter values should be properly displayed in the HTML viewer.
SR: Fix the issue causing the second parameter value to not be displayed in the cascading parameter group in the HTML viewer.
